title: Two Sides: Sorry I was late I was turning in my winning Powerball ticket
description: Mike went on a date with Sally to Texas Roadhouse.  They had great conversation, were there for almost 2 hours and after words he thought they would be planning date 2 soon.  Well now Sally has stopped responding to his texts and he's wondering what happened.
